//Hoffa Fat body

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft parts of Knee MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Hoffa Fat body' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fragmentation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fibrosis ("cyclops lesion")' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hypertrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cartilage-isointense nodulus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickening infrapatellar plica' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Edema' checkbox
Then 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Focal' radio button
Then 'Distal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dorsal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Proximal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Superolateral' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Superolateral' checkbox
Then 'Maltracking of the patella' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Fibrosis ("cyclops lesion")' checkbox
Then 'Low SI in T1w' checkbox is enabled
And 'Low SI in T2w' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Cartilage-isointense nodulus' checkbox
Then '> 1 lesion' checkbox is enabled